data.description: Discover the comfort and charm within this Palm Valley gem! As you step inside, a delightful foyer greets you, complemented by a seamless blend of exquisite wood flooring, neutral tile, and plush carpeting. The heart of this home lies within its impeccable kitchen, boasting an inviting breakfast bar. Adorned with quality wood cabinets, stainless appliances, and a pantry for added storage. Primary Suite offers large walk-in shower, soaking tub, double sinks, and huge walk-in closet. There are two guest bedrooms, and a large office/den. Backyard boasts an inviting patio, and low maintenance landscaping. Home is located in a gated community, surrounded by the 27 hole, championship, Palm Valley Golf Course. Surrounded by shops and restaurants, near I10, with quick access to downtown Phoenix.
